00702 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
00703 /// Bit 0: stallGuardTM status
00704 /// (1: threshold reached)
00705 /// Bit 1: Overtemperature
00706 /// (1: driver is shut down due to overtemperature)
00707 /// Bit 2: Pre-warning overtemperature
00708 /// (1: Threshold is exceeded)
00709 /// Bit 3: Short to ground A
00710 /// (1: Short condition etected, driver currently shut down)
00711 /// Bit 4: Short to ground B
00712 /// (1: Short condition detected, driver currently shut down)
00713 /// Bit 5: Open load A
00714 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00715 /// Bit 6: Open load B
00716 /// (1: no chopper event has happened during the last period with constant coil polarity)
00717 /// Bit 7: Stand still
00718 /// (1: No step impulse occurred on the step input during the last 2^20 clock cycles)
00719 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
